comments: Mitchell (SAC) maintains a legal guarding position defending Lillard (POR) on the perimeter.
Jones (SAC) and Nurkic (POR) engage and disengage during the rebound.
Bagley III (SAC) moves into Lillard (POR) and makes body contact that affects his SQBR.

call_type: Turnover:  Out of Bounds - Bad Pass Turn
comments: Hield (SAC) is the last player to touch the ball after he throws it out of bounds.
McCollum (POR) is the last player to touch the ball when he lands out of bounds.
Bagley III (SAC) closes out to the side of Little (POR) and any contact as he returns to the floor is marginal.

As the Kings go to inbound the ball, they are granted a timeout request.  An assistant coach is the one who asked for the timeout and not the head coach, therefore the timeout request should not have been granted, resulting in a violation by the Kings.
Powell (POR) commits a take foul on Jones (SAC).
McCollum (POR) does not release the throw-in within five seconds.
Nurkic (POR) commits a take foul on Hield (SAC).
Harkless (SAC) and Lillard (POR) make incidental foot to foot contact with each other after Lillard makes the pass.
Hield (SAC) legally contests Little's (POR) jump shot attempt.  Any "high-five" contact after the release is considered incidental.
McCollum (POR) commits a take foul on Hield (SAC).
Jones (SAC) reaches in and makes contact to Lillard's (POR) arm that affects his SQBR.
